title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Feb 16 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Feb 16 2022
description:
Even San Francisco parents are sick of woke school boards. Nolan Peterson joins Clay and Buck to give us a report from on the ground in Ukraine. He warns: "Russia now has enough military firepower on Ukraine's borders to execute sort of the worst-case scenario." Biden under 50% approval in California. Walensky and Fauci: We're not done with masks. The 20% of the country paranoid about covid can ruin life for everyone.
